data.description:
You work for a Marketing Agency and the boss asked you to work on some brochures for the agencies clients. Your task is to format the data for the upcoming projects. So take in an object, 
```javascript
var currentInventory = [
  {
    name: 'Baskin Robbins',
    products: [
      {name: 'Rocky-Road Waffle Cone', price: 8},
      {name: 'Vanilla Double Scoop Waffle Cone', price: 11},
      {name: 'Mint Sprinkles Single Scoop Chocolate Chip Cookie', price: 6},
      {name: 'Orange Serbert Single Scoop Chunky Cheesecake Surprise', price: 4}
    ]
  },
  {
    name: 'Oliver Dairy',
    products: [
      {name: 'Single Scooped Mint Chocolate Death', price: 9},
      {name: 'Triple Scooped Caramel Flashbak', price: 6.95}
    ]
  }
];
```

and have it return in this format
```javascript
var expected = [ 
  'Baskin Robbins, Rocky-Road Waffle Cone, 8',
  'Baskin Robbins, Vanilla Double Scoop Waffle Cone, 11',
  'Baskin Robbins, Mint Sprinkles Single Scoop Chocolate Chip Cookie, 6',
  'Baskin Robbins, Orange Serbert Single Scoop Chunky Cheesecake Surprise, 4',
  'Oliver Dairy, Single Scooped Mint Chocolate Death, 9',
  'Oliver Dairy, Triple Scooped Caramel Flashbak, 6.95' 
];
```


Good Luck.
